comment.body:
A function which i can delete my content is missing in ZeroVoat and IFS too!And that's a big problem!!!
A search function which i can search the topics It would be useful.

The best modern forum software in ZeroNet, but its need more development.Its have modern picture and file share,modern HTML5 video embed function.Unlike ZeroTalk and ZT clones.
For me 3 functions are missing in the forum software.
1.Not just edit but delete topics and comments in ZeroVoat.
On IFS i can edit if i create a channel but i can not delete it!
Its not a bug,this is a missing function.On ZeroTalk i can edit and delete too all what I share.
2.If have the Embed URL from IFS have in topics why this function not have in comments.
3.A search function which people can search the forum topics It would be useful.If possible searching keywords in comments would be the best.The forum would be more transparent a function like this.See on ZeroTorrent.bit.The search function are missing almost all forums in ZeroNet.

I think here is everything have what we need for a modern forum.But these three things are really missing for me.
